Begin now to fix your minds more firmly upon Jesus and heavenly things,
we need to learn the art of trusting our very best Friend. Although we see Him not,
do not let your lips utter one complaining, repining word.
No one in his great need ever looked to Him in faith and was disappointed.
and He is touched with the feeling of our infirmities.
Jesus is watching over us with tender compassion;
